## Notes

- Prioritise issues by impact: broken canonicals and crawl blocks first, cosmetic improvements last.
- Always provide copy-ready fixes, not just descriptions of problems.
- Treat blocked AI crawlers as Critical severity — they cut off the site from AI search entirely.
- Brand authority on Reddit and Wikipedia correlates ~3x stronger with AI citation than backlinks.
- When generating dollar-value estimates, be conservative, state assumptions clearly, and never guarantee specific results.
